OL,5, The chief executive of the Post Office,
OL,6, Nick Read, will return part of his     
OL,7, #450,000 bonus for last year, after a  
OL,8, rebuke from the chairman of the inquiry
OL,9, into the Horizon computer scandal.     
OL,11,FIn its financial accounts for last year
OL,12,Fthe Post Office said its executives had
OL,13,Fmet all their obligations to support   
OL,14,Fthe inquiry into the system.           
OL,16,FBut the inquiry is still taking place. 
OL,18,FThey also wrongly said inquiry chairman
OL,19,FSir Wyn Williams had approved bonuses  
OL,20,Frelating to that support.              
